%TUTORIAL ----------- IPCS - Subcommand VERBEXIT PRSCD ----------------
%Command ===>_ZCMD
%
%PRSCD+formats the Status Collection Data (SCD) control blocks used in H
+detection.
+
+For MVS/XA it will format the Hot I/O Detection Table (HIDT). Then, for
+hot channel path, the SCD will be formatted, including the Interrupt Re
+Block (IRB) for the hot device.
+
+For MVS/370 it will format the SCD, including the device address, inter
+counts, and the time-of-day clock.
)END
